text: The Birth of Venus or Venus Rising (The Star)Gerald M. Ackerman. The life and work of Jean-Léon Gérôme: with a catalogue raisonné. — 1986. — P. 268. () is an 1890 painting by Jean-Léon Gérôme. It depicts the actual birth of Venus from the sea. Sold at auction in 1991. Currently is in a private collection. ==References== Category:Venus Anadyomenes Category:Paintings by Jean-Léon Gérôme Category:Paintings of Venus Category:Nude art Category:1890 paintings Category:Water in art Category:Paintings depicting Greek myths
